{"_path":"/councilor/service/s1009","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"2024年度工作報告：地方建設篇","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s1009-1.jpeg","sequence":1009,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.1 加速宜居城市建設","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1BWJxRFpgB/","author":"牛煦庭","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"牛煦庭"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-02-23T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"_2024-年度工作報告地方建設篇"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2024 年度工作報告：地方建設篇"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"「建設經費大進補，今年各地大開工」"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n等待好幾年的棕線捷運，終於核定，而且照著我在議會的主張，中央補助超過一半。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"即便不算這個超大條的成績，"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"從各部會爭取核定的各項經費，也超過 7 億元"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。以新科立委的第一年來說，算是很有「份量」。\n交通聯外道路打通、人本空間與通學步道佈建、運動中心與設施改善、公園遊具，都留下我們努力的成果。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"選區經營，我們也不落人後，即便立法院動員頻頻，高強度作戰，我們依然積極出席各項活動，做個看得到、找得到的民意代表。我常說，歡迎大家「找事給我做」，因為我一向都用建設和服務，回報鄉親的栽培。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新的一年，我們將配合市府的各項計畫、爭取建設資源，持續改善大家的生活品質！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s1009-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s1009-1.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s1009-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s1009-2.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s1009-3.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s1009-3.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s1009-4.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s1009-4.jpeg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s1009-5.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s1009-5.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"_2024-年度工作報告地方建設篇","depth":2,"text":"2024 年度工作報告：地方建設篇"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s1009.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s1009.md","_extension":"md"}